n係銀行排陣隊又屌，<br />\n野食慢少少又催單。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">巴士黎遲左又鬧個司機。</span><br />\n<br />\n少少幫襯就當自己VIP果野真係好噁心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢個年頭真係要宣揚返互相尊重既概愈念。</blockquote><br />\n呢個抵屌喎 少左班 兩班一齊黎 真係火撚滾</blockquote><br />\n少咗班係抵屌<br />\n兩班一齊嚟通常唔關司機事喎<br />\n係前面嗰班keep住有人上車<br />\n慢慢兩班距離愈來愈近<br />\n塞車就更易發生呢個情況<br />\n唔通你諗住係兩個司機嘆完茶一齊出車咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講起巴士司機我有次幾乎俾佢車死成五十幾公里轉個彎埋站，上到車就見到個司機頭髮留長但係唔梳個人neinei 啡啡咁成程車睇住佢踩油踩break都去到好盡"},{"pid":"ee0fbe78cc4a4a128671f13edc085422b4393dd5","tid":178521,"uid":41466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T03:16:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"562b7f31fc60d4b4747baf913816603d242348e0","tid":178521,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T03:18:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇30秒都知有啲精神問題"},{"pid":"c3d0f29408e126caa2b1277a4d1d3dc6a495b96a","tid":178521,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T03:25:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港客根本低質。<br />\n買野又鍾意R折R贈品RRR，<br />\n係銀行排陣隊又屌，<br />\n野食慢少少又催單。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">巴士黎遲左又鬧個司機。</span><br />\n<br />\n少少幫襯就當自己VIP果野真係好噁心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢個年頭真係要宣揚返互相尊重既概愈念。</blockquote><br />\n呢個抵屌喎 少左班 兩班一齊黎 真係火撚滾</blockquote><br />\n少左班可能係果日人手根本唔夠，未必關司機事，兩班一齊黎可以係塞車/太多客上落遲左或者其他原因，你點肯定係巴士佬錯？"},{"pid":"9bd2355ffe51b3d7696db792c2696d4416d09db3","tid":178521,"uid":953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T03:29:17.000Z","msg":"比人鬧個個同你地cap 個個唔係同一位黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c85bb7d2cd40ea14ba633b8cf43c7a9c19d503d2","tid":178521,"uid":94402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T03:43:22.000Z","msg":"照咁睇，其實唔關化妝小姐同埋啲產品事，應該係佢老公搞到佢咁失常。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋化妝品係遮掩修飾作用，護膚品但凡一搽就見效果啲，多數都係俾個短期效果呃你，唔會真係改善到膚質，係望落去好似改善左，真係一搽就美白果啲，當自己皮膚係用漂白水浸衫咁咩，想快不如學去漂膚吧啦，但會唔會致癌就後果自負。<br />\n而抗氧化，係未氧化之前已經要keep住用，唔係等殘左先黎用，而個效果可能要十幾二十年之後，同番同年紀嘅人比較先睇到係咪真係抗氧化抗衰老成功，仲有好多因素影響，例如生活習慣、飲食、運動、基因遺傳等等，如果唔係女人錢點解咁易賺，家下乜都話抗氧化，抗衰老產品仲賣得特別貴。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72635f7626f64bcd031d84910bb37b5bd80608b9","tid":178521,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T03:44:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實應該係精神有問題嘅客黎......<br />\n通常都係前員工 然後比人炒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就開始瘋狂去舊公司發癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得係俾佢老公搞到short左<br />\n咁啱發作啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n體諒下啦<br />\n其實都好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n體諒? 巴打你邊度返工? 比你體驗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac92c386be9658e44b387beb45caf21642df8e8","tid":178521,"uid":50071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T03:46:40.000Z","msg":"樓上做咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 放低粒seed或者番號先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dce0af42b7e1b57760f3cfc16732fb3a45e353e","tid":178521,"uid":19408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T04:08:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://na.cx/i/XU4T7u8.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXU4T7u8.jpg&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7sPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=ae5125aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/XU4T7u8.jpg</a></blockquote><br />\nBam<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f